    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/4848949/" class="title-link">孔子：未必孤独的哲人</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-4848949"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/iamapig/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1409414-2.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/iamapig/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">瘦猪</span>
